query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(a1 acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select count(*)
from tag AS t1
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.name IN ('2013',
'grammar',
'meaning',
'meaning-in-context',
'sharepoint-enterprise',
'sharepoint-online',
'sharepoint-server',
'visas',
'word-usage') AND s.site_name IN ('ell',
'gaming',
'sharepoint',
'travel')
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.id = a1.question_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND q1.view_count >= 0 AND q1.view_count <= 100
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 10 AND u1.downvotes <= 100000
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name ilike '%gr%';
